reviewText: We love English movies, however it would not be everyone's cup of tea. A strange but enjoyable movie

I have seen it several times long ago, and always enjoyed it. I am glad, at last, to have it in my DVD library. Alec Guinness at his gently comedic best, but as always with a nice moral ticking away underneath. A golden, British oldie.
this dvd won't play on my system. should have read more reviews. my bad. i would have loved to see this film. i remember it from my youth.
